      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "凭信取用，凭信摸你，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "凭信应用你丰富；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我的全人向你开启，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你之所是向我注。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "摸你，就得生命供应，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "借着你灵的运行；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你灵将我纯洁、充盈，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "使我得享你丰盛。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "摸你，恩主，摸你更深，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "摸而取用你丰盛；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "从你接受，恩上加恩，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我就流露你生命。"
            }
          ]
        }
